<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880824-0057 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business: Johnson Worldwide Associates Inc. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> JWAIA </CO><IN> STK </IN><TEXT>   JOHNSON WORLDWIDE ASSOCIATES Inc., Racine, Wis., said it is offering 1,484,224 shares of its Class A common stock at $19.50 each. The maker of recreational products said of the shares being offered, 500,000 shares are being sold by the company and the balance by shareholders. Johnson, which has about 6.2 million Class A common shares outstanding, said its proceeds will be used to reduce debt. William Blair andamp; Co. is leading the underwriting syndicate. </TEXT></DOC>